    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis remains rigid with proactive subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. Finished in concours-level Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle exhibits zero cowl shake or suspension play, riding on factory Style 67 forged wheels. A true turnkey specimen for the discerning collector.",
