      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its original deep-gloss finish without a single rock chip or swirl mark in the paint. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, and the interior still carries that distinctive new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented at authorized dealerships. It features low original miles, a smooth-shifting transmission, and a suspension that provides a tight, responsive ride. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or a discerning driver to own a vehicle in unrivaled condition. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a clean title.",
