      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so you\u2019re getting a total gem that drives like a dream. It\u2019s been garage-kept and loved, and I'm sure you'll love it too. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a look!",
