    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a superlative example of BMW M\u2019s high-revving zenith. At its heart lies the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a cross-plane crankshaft that delivers linear power up to a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and M-variable differential lock operating with factory-spec precision. This vehicle has been maintained to a fastidious standard; the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014common points of concern\u2014have been addressed preventatively using OEM+ components. The exterior showcases original paint depth and clarity, while the cabin's Novillo leather remains supple with no bolster compression or wear on the touchpoints. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
